   Enaidy Reynosa and Urcos, Walther Hernan Casimiro and Alejo, Gelber
   Sebasti Pacovilca},
Title = {DIGITAL SKILLS AND TEACHING PERFORMANCE OF THE NATIONAL UNIVERSITY OF
   EDUCATION IN TIMES OF COVID 19},
